<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<!--<![endif]-->
<!-- start: HEAD -->
<head>
	<title>[check] 서비스 점검중</title>
	<!-- start: META -->
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
	<meta content="" name="description" />
	<meta content="" name="author" />
	<!-- end: META -->
	<style>
		body, html {background:#f6f6f6}
		.error__wrap {text-align:center}
		.error__wrap-content {width:500px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:200px}
		.error__icon {font-size:30px;font-family: "Arial", arial,sans-serif;color:#fff;width:30px;height:30px;text-align:center;line-height: 30px;margin:0 auto;background: #2572ce;padding:7px;}
		.error__title {color:#333;font-family: Avenir,'Lato',"애플 SD 산돌고딕 Neo","Apple SD Gothic Neo","나눔바른고딕",NanumBarunGothic,"나눔고딕",NanumGothic,"맑은 고딕","Malgun Gothic","돋움",dotum,AppleGothic,sans-serif}
		.error__desc {color:#999;line-height:1.8}
		.error__detail-box {width:500px;margin:20px auto;text-align:left;border:1px solid #ccc;border-width:1px 0;}
		.error__detail-box:before{display:block;height:1px;background:#eee;content:''}
		.error__detail-box:after{display:block;height:1px;background:#eee;content:''}
		.error__detail-box li {padding:5px 0}
	</style>
</head>
<!-- end: HEAD -->
<body>
<div class="error__wrap">
	<div class="error__wrap-content">
		<!-- start: 콘텐츠 -->
		<div class="adm-error">
			<div class="error__icon">!</div>
			<h1 class="error__title">서비스 점검</h1>
			<p class="error__desc">
				안녕하세요. hidden 운영팀입니다.<br>
				서비스 업데이트를 위하여 아래와 같이 점검이 진행되며<br>
				점검 시간 동안 서비스 이용이 제한됩니다.
			</p>
			<div class="error__detail-box">
				<ul>
					<li>
						<span>점검시간 : </span>
						<span>{{ period }}</span>
					</li>
					<li>
						<span>점검내용 : </span>
						<span>{{ reason }}</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<p class="error__desc">
				더 나은 서비스를 위해 노력하겠습니다.<br>
				감사합니다.
			</p>

		</div>
		<!-- end: 콘텐츠 -->
	</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
